name: Crochet Minnie Mouse Beanie
description:
This Minnie Mouse Beanie is a perfect accessory for photo shoots and gift for a Disney fan, or just for your own enjoyment to adorn you sweet newborn baby or child with! The beanie comes in all sizes from infants to adults.  

All hats/beanies are custom made to fit your style and color.  If you desire another color please respond in the comment box when checking out.

Preemie/Newborn: (up to about 3 weeks) 13" circumference
0-3 Months: 14 - 15" (with stretch) circumference
3-6 Months: 15 - 17" (with stretch) circumference
6-12 Months: 16 - 19" (with stretch) circumference
1-2 and 3-4 Years: 18 - 20" (with stretch) circumference
5-10 Years: 19 - 20.5" (with stretch) circumference
Teen/Adult: 20.5 - 22" (with stretch) circumference

Care: Machine wash warm, gentle cycle. Tumble dry low. Do not over dry. For best results on fringe, hand wash; lay flat to dry.

Shipping: Items are shipped within 5-7 days of purchase.
